{
  "stem": "21788.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I guess I went there with friends, and possibly also with my sister.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This is rather vague in my memory of it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I just remember that my father started an apartment, and possibly his practice as a dentist, in the-- well, in the suburb of Berlin, which was a very nice place called Buckow Markische Schweiz.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This was a destination to come over the weekend to relax, to swim, to bathe.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I guess my father saw an opportunity in Buckow to become the local dentist.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was no dentist there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He started this in 1925.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He married in 1927.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I came along in 1928.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And my father then also had a practice as a dentist in Berlin.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The summers in Berlin where quite uncomfortable-- hot, muggy, humid.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And so, because my father had this apartment in Buckow, we spent the summer months in Buckow, and I also went to school over there.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "My father stayed in Berlin because that was his main practice-- practiced dentistry during the week.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Friday afternoon he took his one-cylinder car, the long trip to Buckow, which was cobble-- cobblestone highways-- streets, in that time.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "When he came to Buckow, about 6 o'clock in the afternoon on Friday, he came through-- we're talking a very small place.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Right now Buckow has 1,400 inhabitants.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We visited just two years ago.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It might have been a little bit bigger, or it might have been a little bit smaller at that time.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Anyway, when he came through main street, which was Berliner Strasse, he honked his horn, and everybody knew the dentist is, is in town.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they came, and waited in line to get the service.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, we stayed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We stayed in Buckow over the summer months.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
